<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The corporation is liable for the acts of its officers and agents acting within the scope of their authority.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id74a14532-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1418">112 Stat. 1418</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
